{"tid":1865384,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"鼻敏感載口罩真係好撚辛苦","createTime":"2020-02-06T07:03:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T14:00:36.000Z","uid":259044,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e418a46c2407e94994a60a9d886fe0e48716b943","tid":1865384,"uid":259044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T07:03:23.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鼻塞</span></span></strong><br />\n本身已經唔太抖到氣 <br />\n載住個口罩仲難呼吸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用口抖氣又會吸到個口罩 <br />\n有時打完乞嗤或者流過鼻水嚟仲會掂到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 極唔舒服<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鼻痕</span></span></strong><br />\n如果載緊嗰陣鼻痕 咁就仆街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n忍住唔R好辛苦 R又俾人望住 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個個褪後幾步咪話唔怕羞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">流鼻水</span></span></strong><br />\n如果咁啱有帶紙巾都話好啲 除開個罩抹乾淨就得<br />\n如果無帶就奶閪了 <br />\n一係就係咁嗦住 唔俾佢流落嚟<br />\n一係就用條唎奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔通有佢流咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用衫抺又俾人印象污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用唎奶有返罩遮住人地睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係咁打乞嗤</span></span></strong><br />\n事關我係忍開乞嗤嗰派 有時個鼻痕起上嚟連打十個都唔誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係點忍都好 點會有聲 人地都睇得出你打緊乞嗤<br />\n連發嗰陣就好似用發出殺氣咁 個個都即刻退讓三分<br />\n吸引途人眼光 個個都望住你 好似歧視咁 點會好受<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲都係鼻敏感 應該身同感受"},{"pid":"b77a384abc036b496dab041718365b575b3d4ec3","tid":1865384,"uid":259044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T07:07:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鼻塞</span></span></strong><br />\n本身已經唔太抖到氣 <br />\n載住個口罩仲難呼吸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用口抖氣又會吸到個口罩 <br />\n有時打完乞嗤或者流過鼻水嚟仲會掂到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 極唔舒服<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鼻痕</span></span></strong><br />\n如果載緊嗰陣鼻痕 咁就仆街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n忍住唔R好辛苦 R又俾人望住 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個個褪後幾步咪話唔怕羞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">流鼻水</span></span></strong><br />\n如果咁啱有帶紙巾都話好啲 除開個罩抹乾淨就得<br />\n如果無帶就奶閪了 <br />\n一係就係咁嗦住 唔俾佢流落嚟<br />\n一係就用條唎奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔通有佢流咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用衫抺又俾人印象污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用唎奶<span style=\"color: red;\">返有</span>罩遮住人地睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係咁打乞嗤</span></span></strong><br />\n事關我係忍開乞嗤嗰派 有時個鼻痕起上嚟連打十個都唔誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係點忍都好 <span style=\"color: red;\">都</span>會有聲 人地都睇得出你打緊乞嗤<br />\n連發嗰陣就好似發出殺氣咁 個個都即刻退讓三分<br />\n吸引途人眼光 個個都望住你 好似歧視咁 點會好受<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲都係鼻敏感 應該身同感受</blockquote>"},{"pid":"f1d89aade2edda6b18285679fd9b0c1d2e36fea2","tid":1865384,"uid":76135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T07:11:30.000Z","msg":"唯有食重抗敏藥"},{"pid":"e510572b966bc8494f9b8df31d75d4e0217dd6a6","tid":1865384,"uid":275339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T07:17:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"502219d37b2631b3330cd183a8d521049b1606f2","tid":1865384,"uid":8330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T07:18:40.000Z","msg":"身同感受 到底仲要繼續戴口罩幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d00415aadd6e73bceb87a62207cdede94a1f7c58","tid":1865384,"uid":131843,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T07:26:28.000Z","msg":"我反而舒服咗，明顯係因為擋晒過敏原<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02196822f925d218940272e4152803c4031bb879","tid":1865384,"uid":259044,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d00415aadd6e73bceb87a62207cdede94a1f7c58","tid":1865384,"uid":131843,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T07:26:28.000Z","msg":"我反而舒服咗，明顯係因為擋晒過敏原<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T07:28:53.000Z","msg":"載住會無咁易有徵狀係真<br />\n但係一嚟料就慘到喊<br />\n特別係 係咁打乞嗤 真係頂唔順人地個眼光"},{"pid":"72ddc9507b68d9970ff3f277dd0d6b2be5fb0df1","tid":1865384,"uid":324984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T07:32:47.000Z","msg":"忍開乞嗤嗰派... ...<br />\n千萬不要忍. 乞嗤是身體想把外物排出一個途徑. 有個在台灣學醫的朋友曾經告訴我, 乞嗤其實是好東西.<br />\n我都有鼻敏感. 可能無巴的嚴重, 不過長時間(其實只係一兩個鐘)都覺得焗和頭痛.<br />\n有日在小巴上見到個姨姨對住個面撥扇... ...相信是因為她覺得焗, 不過其實好危險."},{"pid":"585f70450314d57b160af31178c8ff61515972c7","tid":1865384,"uid":259044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72ddc9507b68d9970ff3f277dd0d6b2be5fb0df1","tid":1865384,"uid":324984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T07:32:47.000Z","msg":"忍開乞嗤嗰派... ...<br />\n千萬不要忍. 乞嗤是身體想把外物排出一個途徑. 有個在台灣學醫的朋友曾經告訴我, 乞嗤其實是好東西.<br />\n我都有鼻敏感. 可能無巴的嚴重, 不過長時間(其實只係一兩個鐘)都覺得焗和頭痛.<br />\n有日在小巴上見到個姨姨對住個面撥扇... ...相信是因為她覺得焗, 不過其實好危險."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T07:39:38.000Z","msg":"如果唔忍會打到聲沙+喉嚨痛<img src=\"/a