Z","msg":"忍開乞嗤嗰派... ...<br />\n千萬不要忍. 乞嗤是身體想把外物排出一個途徑. 有個在台灣學醫的朋友曾經告訴我, 乞嗤其實是好東西.<br />\n我都有鼻敏感. 可能無巴的嚴重, 不過長時間(其實只係一兩個鐘)都覺得焗和頭痛.<br />\n有日在小巴上見到個姨姨對住個面撥扇... ...相信是因為她覺得焗, 不過其實好危險."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T07:39:38.000Z","msg":"如果唔忍會打到聲沙+喉嚨痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T13:50:38.000Z","msg":"這是真. 不過也不要忍得太緊要. <br />\n身體健康啊!"},{"pid":"34d3bc7b63ac276ef0f45e0f1ca36f623105c830","tid":1865384,"uid":98700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6ee13034f90b1372350da1c37b664b11f22c18e","tid":1865384,"uid":294031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T08:37:08.000Z","msg":"我一時時嚟料<br />\n一嚟就大鑊嘢<br />\n不過尼排買咗日本抗敏藥，超有效///<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f1YXc8k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff1YXc8k.png&h=c7c4715b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可以試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T06:24:59.000Z","msg":"食完係咪會好眼瞓？"},{"pid":"6af29c960937add0ef8df1124569d3b9573dac3b","tid":1865384,"uid":49151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T06:25:43.000Z","msg":"我覺得戴咗口罩冇咁嚴重"},{"pid":"7839dc39b24a9ddc367746a693f76e0cc3d54da6","tid":1865384,"uid":123115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e418a46c2407e94994a60a9d886fe0e48716b943","tid":1865384,"uid":259044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T07:03:23.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鼻塞</span></span></strong><br />\n本身已經唔太抖到氣 <br />\n載住個口罩仲難呼吸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用口抖氣又會吸到個口罩 <br />\n有時打完乞嗤或者流過鼻水嚟仲會掂到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 極唔舒服<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鼻痕</span></span></strong><br />\n如果載緊嗰陣鼻痕 咁就仆街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj